  "short_description": "Ready, set, mix! The Mixologist is a VR bartending game where you'll craft cocktails and serve customers. Enjoy over 100 recipes in 5 different bars and play through a dynamic solo career or team up with friends in co-op mode to speed up your progress and become the ultimate mixologist!",
