atic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/b0cd6d39f0502ab39381a6a8ca96ac11.poster.avif?t=1731691157\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/b0cd6d39f0502ab39381a6a8ca96ac11.webm?t=1731691157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/b0cd6d39f0502ab39381a6a8ca96ac11.mp4?t=1731691157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/348e7243d540c34a501bb457438ffb5c.webp?t=1731691157\" width=540 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/93acda5fb51ac7fa259d06c43d172a37.poster.avif?t=1731691157\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/93acda5fb51ac7fa259d06c43d172a37.webm?t=1731691157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/93acda5fb51ac7fa259d06c43d172a37.mp4?t=1731691157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Why Mixologist?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Mixologist combines fast-paced challenges with the fun of mastering your bartending skills. Whether playing solo or with friends in co-op mode, you’ll find a blend of creativity, strategy, and fun that keeps the good times rolling! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join the Community:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect with other players and share your bartending journey. Compete on global leaderboards, exchange tips and tricks, and become part of the vibrant Mixologist community.</p>",
